# Trouvez une commande qui permet, en temps réel, de trouver
# les processus en cours d'exécution [Commande]
top

# Use top or ps to view the active processes.
# top is like Window's Task Manager: it gives real time data about memory usage, CPU,
# buffers and active processes.
# ps gives a static list of active processes. Flags can be used to filter the list.
